Title: Mutational Signature Comprehensive Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.99.1
Authors@R: c(person("Aaron", "Chevalier", email = "atgc@bu.edu", role = "cre", comment = c(ORCHID = "0000-0002-3968-9250")), person(given=c("Joshua","D."), family="Campbell", email="camp@bu.edu", role=c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0780-8662")))
Description: The Mutational Signature TookKit has utilities for extracting variants from a variety of file formats, contains multiple methods for discovery of novel signatures or prediction of known signatures, as well as many types of downstream visualizations for exploratory analysis.
